<F P=100> RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin Said To Approve Military Bases in CIS, Latvia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin Said To Approve Military Bases in CIS, Latvia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0604143394 Moscow 2x2 Television in Russian 1330 GMT 6 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0604143394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow 2x2 Television </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Boris Yeltsin has approved a Defense Ministry 
proposal on creating Russian Armed Forces military bases on the 
territory of CIS countries and Latvia to ensure their common 
security and also to test new weapons and military equipment. 
  The president has instructed the Foreign and Defense 
Ministries to hold talks with these states in order to achieve 
the necessary agreements. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

