  [Text] Stepanakert ("LRAGIR", "AZG" dailies), 03/30/94--The 
Azeri units shelled, using different weaponry, particularly 
Howitzers, mortars and armored infantry carriers, the Armenian 
positions in the Askeranskiy district and at the villages of 
Salakhli-Kengerli, Papravend, Shakbulakh and Novruzlu in the 
Agdamskiy district. The shelling started in the night of March 
