Karabakh] Defense Army Political Department Rudolf Martirosyan 
rejected the information spread by the Azeri media on 
mercenaries from Lebanon, Syria, Palestine and the PKK [Kurdish 
Workers Party] groups who are ostensibly fighting at the 
Armenian side. According to the Political Department, such 
misinformation is spread in order to justify the participation 
of Afghan mojahedins, Russian and Ukrainian mercenaries fighting 
in the Azeri army. 

