<H3> <TI>   New Security Forces To Tackle Local Drug Problem </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Security Forces To Tackle Local Drug Problem </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0804081494 Tbilisi SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA in Russian 31 Mar 94 
p 4 </F>

<F P=103> AU0804081494 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [GIA report under the rubric "According to Reports From </F>
Correspondents and Information Agencies": "In the Struggle 
Against the Narcotics Business"] 
  [Text] On 29 March, a meeting of the recently created 
coordinating headquarters of the law enforcement bodies in the 
Kartli region was held in Gori. The heads of the region's law 
enforcement structures participated in its work. On account of 
the worsening situation concerning the narcotics business, 
methods of resolving this problem were outlined at the meeting 
and a plan of action was adopted. In this regard, mixed groups 
made up of representatives of the Ministry of Security, the 
military police, and the Ministry of Internal Affairs were 
created. These forces will control all points of entry into and 
out of Tskhinvali [administrative center of south Ossetia] in 
order to prevent narcotic substances from coming into the 
republic from the northern Caucasus. 

</TEXT>

