<H3> <TI>   `Humanitarian Party' Founded; Ministry Reviewing Platform </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Humanitarian Party' Founded; Ministry Reviewing Platform </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS0704193494 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1715 
GMT 7 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS0704193494 </F>
<F P=104>  Minsk Radio Minsk Network </F>
<F P=105>  Belarusian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The organizational committee of a new party has 
been established in Belarus -- the Belarusian Humanitarian 
Party. Kanstantsin Syalchonak, known to many of our listeners as 
an astropsychologist, has been elected chairman of the new 
party. Although the party has already held its constituent 
congress, its statute and program are still being examined by 
the Ministry of Justice. The party founders are convinced that 
they will contribute to the quick and effective improvement of 
our lives. 

</TEXT>

