  [Excerpts] Azerbaijan's Foreign Ministry said that 
financial difficulties have forced the Iraqi Government to close 
its embassy in the capital of Azerbaijan. [passage omitted] 
  (Shaykh ol-Eslam Shukrallah Pashazada), the religious leader 
