<H3> <TI>   Kravchuk Praises Talks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kravchuk Praises Talks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS0704184394 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in 
Ukrainian 1800 GMT 7 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS0704184394 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] If the Polish-Ukrainian talks provide good results 
on such delicate issues as defense, this testifies to the fact 
that relations between our people and states are based on 
understanding and confidence. This was said by Ukrainian 
President Leonid Kravchuk during a meeting with Polish Defense 
Minister Piotr Kolodziejczyk. The head of the Ukrainian state 
and the chief of the Polish defense department discussed a wide 
range of issues concerning deepening [word indistinct] 
cooperation, including defense, as well as protecting peace and 
stability in the region. 
  The official visit of the Polish Armed Forces delegation to 
Ukraine continues. Today, the Polish servicemen also met with 
Deputy Prime Minister Valeriy Shmarov, and visited the Kiev 
Military Institute of Administration and Communication and the 
Antonov Scientific Technical Center. 

