new structure under the president headed by Petr Filippov, from 
now on intends to regularly inform the press precisely on 
everyday administrative matters. The journalists that were 
invited to today's news conference in the former CPSU building 
were promised access to all the sub-departments of the service 
and to all officials. Petr Filippov promised that those 
officials of the presidential staff that refuse to give an 
interview will be made to do it, but not by using methods 
favored by the former owners of these halls. 

