  [Text] Belarusian Defense Minister Colonel General Pavel 
Kazlowski, while touring Homel Oblast this week, visited Russian 
military units stationed in the area and held negotiations with 
representatives of the Russian Armed Forces. During those 
negotiations, conditions for the withdrawal of Russian troops 
from Belarusian territory, as well as the fate of military 
quarters and property, were addressed. 

