<F P=104>  Bishkek Kyrgyz Radio First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Kyrgyz </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A routine meeting of the city council [kenesh] of 
people's deputies was held today in Bishkek. The meeting 
examined the following issues: 
  1. Implementation of the program for socioeconomic reforms 
and anticrisis measures in Bishkek, which was adopted on 2 April 
1993 at the 15th session of the Bishkek city council of people's 
deputies; amendments to the program in the light of the Kyrgyz 
Government's 24 April 1994 resolution No. 84 for furthering 
economic reforms and measures aimed at putting into practice a 
presidential decree of 10 April 1994; and urgent measures aimed 
at strengthening state and financial discipline. 
  2. Endorsement of a comprehensive program by the Bishkek 
city administration for the targeted social protection of 
citizens in 1994-95. 

</TEXT>

