<F P=100> RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Ministry Wants UN Peacekeepers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ministry Wants UN Peacekeepers </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1104134894 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1328 GMT 11 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1104134894 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Moscow April 11 TASS - Russia suggested on Monday 
that a contingent of UN peacekeepers be sent urgently to 
Gorazde. The Foreign Ministry also called in a statement to 
withdraw Serb troops from the besieged Moslem enclave and for 
"the demilitarization of the safety zone, including the 
disarming of Moslem units acting in the area". 
  "We see the task of the UN Security Council in actively 
promoting these goals", the statement said. 

</TEXT>

