<H3> <TI>   Abkhazian Reconnaissance Group Said `Eliminated' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Abkhazian Reconnaissance Group Said `Eliminated' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1004143794 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1322 GMT 10 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1004143794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow INTERFAX </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Georgian formations eliminated an Abkhazian 
reconnaissance group of five men in the Kodor Ravine, the 
Georgian Defense Ministry told Interfax. Georgia has not 
sustained any losses. According to the same source, helicopters 
evacuated about 60 civilians from the high-mountain villages of 
Abkhazian Svanetia (the Kodor Ravine). 
  Since fighting began in the Kodor Ravine last March, more 
than a thousand Georgians have abandoned their native villages. 
No information about the situation in the Kodor Ravine has 
arrived from the Abkhazian Defense Ministry yet. 

</TEXT>

