a consultation on the peaceful settlement of Azeri-Armenian 
conflict. 
  The informed sources announced to TURAN that Kazimirov will 
present the leadership of Armenia some initiatives, which prior 
was presented to the Azeri leadership during his visit to Baku 
on April 6. 
  The consultation with the participance of all the sides of 
conflict will be continued in Prague on April 11-15. 

