<F P=100> Georgia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Parliament on Georgian-Abkhazian Friendship </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Parliament on Georgian-Abkhazian Friendship </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0804181994 Yerevan SNARK in English 1156 GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0804181994 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan SNARK </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Moscow, April 8 (SNARK)--Debates between deputies of 
the Georgian Parliament finished with the consensus--the 
majority of deputies estimated the Moscow negotiations and the 
concluded agreements as positive. The opposition annulled the 
question of the agreements dissolution, Georgian Embassy in 
Moscow told SNARK. 
  Press-Service of the Georgian Parliament issued the 
statement 
which speaks for the necessity of the friendship between 
Georgians and Abkhazians. 

</TEXT>

