<H3> <TI>   Reporting on Black Sea Fleet Attack </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Reporting on Black Sea Fleet Attack </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Response to Cheleken Incident </H4>

<F P=102> LD1104110794 Kiev UNIAR in Ukrainian 0935 GMT 11 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1104110794 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UNIAR </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] Odessa, 11 Apr -- According to the Black Sea 
Fleet press center, about 120 Ukrainian naval servicemen stormed 
the Odessa conservation division of the Black Sea fleet between 
2100 and 2300 on 10 April. [passage omitted] 
  Sources close to Ukraine's Navy headquarters said the action 
was a response to the unlawful conduct by the Black Sea Fleet 
Command Conservation Division 318 and the command of the 
Cheleken hydrographic vessel. The Black Sea Fleet press center 
report on the course of the aforementioned incidents is 
therefore biased and will only aggravate the tension. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

