<H3> <TI>   Turkish Schooner Detained in Sea Economic Zone </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Turkish Schooner Detained in Sea Economic Zone </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0804020594 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 
1900 GMT 7 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0804020594 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The new service of Ukraine's border troops reported 
that a Coast Guard ship detained the Turkish schooner Bayrakhtar 
20 miles from Zmiyinyy Island. The schooner was in Ukraine's 
exclusive sea economic zone with its tackle ready for fishing. 
The schooner was escorted to the frontier post in Kamyshova Bay 
in the city of Sevastopol to undergo full examination. In 
addition, a large number of fishing nets with radar beacons were 
discovered in the vicinity of Zmiyinyy Island. The sea border 
guards keep the entire Black Sea region under observation. 

</TEXT>

