<F P=100> National Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Meshkov Denies Report of Assassination Attempt </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Meshkov Denies Report of Assassination Attempt </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0904164894 Moscow NTV in Russian 1500 GMT 9 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0904164894 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow NTV </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] [Announcer Kiselev] Yuriy Meshkov's press service 
has denied reports that an assassination attempt had been made 
against the president of Crimea, but according to information 
from the Crimea With Ukraine association, the president was shot 
at on 6 April and one of his guards was wounded. 

</TEXT>

